## Client-side (Vite)
VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://your-project.supabase.co
VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=your-anon-key

## Server-side (Vercel env vars — for API proxy)
## These power the AI and audio generation for users without their own keys.
## Set these in Vercel Dashboard > Settings > Environment Variables.
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=your-service-role-key
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# OPENAI_API_KEY=sk-...
# GEMINI_API_KEY=AI...
# ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=...

## Stripe (for credits/billing)
# STRIPE_SECRET_KEY=sk_test_...
# STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET=whsec_...
# STRIPE_PRODUCT_ID=prod_...             # Product ID from Stripe Dashboard (not a price — prices are dynamic)
